{"tid":2020752,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"62國支持對疫情展開獨立調查 ，包括印度尼西亞、日本、韓國、土耳其、俄羅斯、南非和英國在內的62個國家支持該動議。","createTime":"2020-05-17T09:52:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T15:57:05.000Z","uid":179729,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"2faa8378f4832f7c91f3b1d750616ec17e7250e6","tid":2020752,"uid":179729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T09:52:12.000Z","msg":"至關重要的世界衛生大會（World Health Assembly，WHA）明天在日內瓦舉行之際，62個國家共同支持澳大利亞和歐盟聯合發起的對冠狀病毒爆發的獨立調查。<br />\n<br />\n澳大利亞是第一個呼籲對新冠疫情的起源進行獨立調查的國家。<br />\n<br />\n這招致北京的強烈譴責，指責澳大利亞對中國發動政治攻擊。但國際上對這一提議的支持一直在穩步增長。<br />\n<br />\n全文：<a href=\"https://www.abc.net.au/chinese/2020-05-17/coronavirus-australia-latest-news-live-update/12257012\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.abc.net.au%2Fchinese%2F2020-05-17%2Fcoronavirus-australia-latest-news-live-update%2F12257012&d=5MMtl3Q8rD8%2FKomM%2B8e61%2FMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=3c426f46\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.abc.net.au/chinese/2020-05-17/coronavirus-australia-latest-news-live-update/12257012</a>"},{"pid":"f34b1665dae4705d92693f204045109a0829bc13","tid":2020752,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T09:54:09.000Z","msg":"聽日就係對支那嘅審判日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ce09010e48d70ed72ad1923ce273c68b3dbd732","tid":2020752,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T09:54:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又贏"},{"pid":"98156e3f994e28d385ce454066ec453020f67559","tid":2020752,"uid":3776,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T09:55:29.000Z","msg":"咁多個國家你估真心想查咩<br />\n咪又要錢...至於幾多...<br />\n支那大把錢 唔洗怕"},{"pid":"00c492cec5d414e8aec0437aa4926162139e323b","tid":2020752,"uid":122275,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"98156e3f994e28d385ce454066ec453020f67559","tid":202